Program: Omnibus
Title: Making Money
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376k8t
Last Broadcast Date: 17 February 1992
'Money is here to stay'. An exploration of the processes of manufacturing bank notes and coins, including visits to De La Rue, the company that makes 70% of the worlds' bank notes and the Royal Mint. Picture: British pound coins, Credit: Getty Images